results.name: Number of strict integer partitions of n with no 1's and a part divisible by all the other parts.
comment: Alternative name: Number of strict integer partitions of n with no 1's that are empty or have greatest part divisible by all the other parts.
xref: The dual version is A098965 (non-strict: A083711).
The non-strict version is A339619 (Heinz numbers: complement of A343337).
The version with 1's allowed is A343347 (non-strict: A130689).
The case without a part dividing all the other parts is A343380.
A000070 counts partitions with a selected part.
A015723 counts strict partitions with a selected part.
A018818 counts partitions into divisors (strict: A033630).
A167865 counts strict chains of divisors > 1 summing to n.
